[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin se silno raduje

506
00:33:18,799 --> 00:33:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] svakome od vas,

507
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] svakome koji iskreno

508
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] tražite njegovo lice

509
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] i pomoć u njemu.

510
00:33:27,579 --> 00:33:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što može preporoditi

511
00:33:31,599 --> 00:33:32,660
[SPEAKER_00] i moj i Tvoj život

512
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] je upravo ljubav.

513
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav koja navire

514
00:33:38,380 --> 00:33:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] iz srca Isusova,

515
00:33:39,559 --> 00:33:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] koja kaže u svetome pismu

516
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubavlju vječnom Te ljubim

517
00:33:46,339 --> 00:33:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] i zato Ti sačuvah milost.

518
00:33:48,960 --> 00:33:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] Neka se pokrenu planine

519
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] i potrijesu brijezi.

520
00:33:55,220 --> 00:33:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se moja ljubav

521
00:33:56,980 --> 00:33:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] nikada neće odmaći od Tebe.

522
00:33:59,099 --> 00:34:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin je tu.

523
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Draga sestro, dragi brate,

524
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] što god da provaziš u životu,

525
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] nisi sam.

526
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je s tobom.

527
00:34:17,860 --> 00:34:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je sa mnom i sa tobom.

528
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] Zagrli Isusov križ.

529
00:34:26,679 --> 00:34:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dogrliš Isusov križ,

530
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] grliš i prihvaćaš svoju muku.

531
00:34:34,699 --> 00:34:36,280
[SPEAKER_00] sjedini je s Isusovom.

532
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjeti ćeš kako ono što Isus rekao,

533
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] breme je moje slatko,

534
00:34:41,739 --> 00:34:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] breme je moje lako.

535
00:34:43,539 --> 00:34:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Isus s nama dijeli breme,

536
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] breme i teret ovoga svijeta,

537
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] breme i teret naše duše,

538
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] naših obitelji,

539
00:34:55,780 --> 00:34:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] naše crkve.

540
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine,

541
00:35:00,659 --> 00:35:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] neka Tvoje blagoslov siđe na sve njih,

542
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] milost i snaga Duha Svetoga.

543
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] To Te molimo,

544
00:35:09,599 --> 00:35:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] po Kristu,

545
00:35:11,139 --> 00:35:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu našemu.

546
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

